preamble: "\nFor given code blocks from an Android Studio project, suggest improvements for the code.\nLook not only for bugs and potential optimizations, but also for ways to make the code more\nidiomatic or readable. For example, you may suggest renaming things to be more clear.\n\nPrioritize the most important improvements. Some optimizations might have larger impacts than others.\nProvide explanations for each suggestion to help the user understand the rationale and best practices.\nIf necessary, suggest alternative implementations to help them visualize the proposed changes."
